=== Road vehicle slope steepness===
{{en/-}}{{en/Feature|1.1|align="right"|text=(since 1.1.0)}}
Sets the steepness of slopes, road vehicles will slow down more on slopes if this setting is set to a higher value. It only applies if the [[Main/en/Settings/Road vehicle acceleration model|realistic acceleration]] is selected.

;Valid options<nowiki>:</nowiki> [0 <= n <= 10]
: 0: 0% (lowest)
: ...
: <span style="color:blue">'''7: 7% (default)'''</span>
: ...
: 10: 10% (steepest)

;[[Main/en/openttd.cfg]]
:[vehicle]
:roadveh_slope_steepness

